text: Decent bowl of M.H.K.  1st time taste of 'smokiness' in this dish.  S$5.50 for this dry bowl.
First time eating meehoonkway with Wok Hey. Tasty and decent price, definitely worth a try. Should be 4-5 stars but rating dragged down by one 1 star review.

Tried , soup only have anchovies smell. Don't know what vege he put, don't like the smell of the vege. Other meat are smooth . And the eggs are not cooked . Overrated stall.  Just go jurong west area and eat ban mian it's better

Their mee hoon kueh($5.50) is decent and meat portion is big. Overall 7.5/10.
